Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.99,0:23:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么便当啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.86,0:23:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不是便当是学习
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.12,0:23:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I made a mistake
